msg: - Added a message to the request map in failover before sending it to prevent race condition where the response tries (and fails) to remove the message before it is even added. This is to prevent double sending a message because it is still in the requestMap. (This is for the master-slave test cases)
- Enabled a QueueBridgeTest, this test seems to pass already.
